  m_text: '<b>Disclaimer</b>


    Scene Registry is a scene referencing tool, not
    a security system. Regardless of the chosen storage mode, a sufficiently motivated
    user can potentially access build data using decompilation or asset extraction
    tools. It is important to note that <b>this limitation exists independently of
    this package</b>: any Unity build is by nature decompilable, with or without
    Scene Registry. The package developer <b>declines all responsibility</b> in the
    event of cheating, data tampering, or unauthorized access in your project.'
